import {Button, CardBody, CardImg, Card, CardSubtitle, CardText, CardTitle} from "reactstrap";
import React from "react";

function MyCard (){
    return (
    <Card>
        <CardImg
            alt="Card image cap"
            src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
            top
            width="100%"
        />
        <CardBody>
            <CardTitle tag="h5">
                Card title
            </CardTitle>
            <CardSubtitle
                className="mb-2 text-muted"
                tag="h6"
            >
                Card subtitle
            </CardSubtitle>
            <CardText>
                This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
            </CardText>
            <Button>
                Button
            </Button>
        </CardBody>
    </Card>
    );
}
export default MyCard;
